{"tid":1452189,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"潘紹聰嘆人比鬼恐怖","createTime":"2019-08-12T00:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T00:27:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aa82ff49de0d34569cac1c12705a516ba5b0bc29","tid":1452189,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:20:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190812/20747254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F20747254&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARke9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=d6d799e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F20747254&h=1d860838\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190812/20747254</a><br />\n<br />\n潘紹聰嘆人比鬼恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190812/large/1565531330_d790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190812%2Flarge%2F1565531330_d790.jpg&h=b80b2967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n潘紹聰（右）和陳家樂前晚大談靈異經歷。<br />\n<br />\n「鬼王」潘紹聰前晚在尖沙嘴為靈異節目11周年舉行聚餐，邀得電影《綁靈》演員拍檔陳家樂、麥家瑜及岑日珈等到場支持。潘紹聰談到個人最恐怖的經歷：「有次我去印尼探靈，當時蒙住眼，突然感覺到右邊大髀俾人好大力拍咗一下，但其實周圍冇人。事後有啲睇到嘢嘅朋友，見到有隻老虎行過，而當地真係修練好多老虎精。」不過他直指人比鬼恐怖：「最恐怖就係嗰啲冥頑不靈、問極唔答嗰啲人，仲難搞過鬼。我農曆七月十四真係會去燒街衣，喺沙嶺。」<br />\n<br />\n陳家樂分享在大馬住酒店遇上的靈異經歷：「我瞓緊突然感覺到有對手喺床尾壓落黎，聽到有把小朋友聲，喺我耳邊咆哮，即刻嚇醒左。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪、攝影：盧妹  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n鄭秀文着到似糭惹側目<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】翁靜晶細女英教堂行禮"},{"pid":"5c8dd3190cec9ff4f0a73514925a2639ad597629","tid":1452189,"uid":235174,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5QEmXH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5QEmXH.jpg&h=d2e05ead&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1d634db8590014ed503e0e888f715921ce49564","tid":1452189,"uid":76647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:25:45.000Z","msg":"以前好怕鬼 怕晚上番家路又黑又暗<br />\n但六月到依家又嬲又灰到已在完全唔怕黑唔怕鬼"},{"pid":"a0beeac8b9da4c9f64aa294ffacaca08a532ca70","tid":1452189,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f1d634db8590014ed503e0e888f715921ce49564","tid":1452189,"uid":76647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:25:45.000Z","msg":"以前好怕鬼 怕晚上番家路又黑又暗<br />\n但六月到依家又嬲又灰到已在完全唔怕黑唔怕鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:27:49.000Z","msg":"條街點黑都唔夠警畜黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}